 up, but our flow\ncontinuing strictly beyond in these situations.\n  All our constructions of unbounded curvature developing and then disappearing\nare in two dimensions. Generalisations to higher dimensions are then immediate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2013 19:46:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Oct 2014 05:58:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-03"}
